'''Palpatine's private viewing box''' in the [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] was adjacent to [[Romeo Treblanc's private viewing box|Romeo Treblanc's]].

==History==
The viewing box was reserved for the [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and other politicians of the government, such as the [[Senior Administrative Aide]] [[Sly Moore/Legends|Sly Moore]] and the [[Vice Chair/Legends|Vice Chair]] [[Mas Amedda/Legends|Mas Amedda]]. [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] could also invite other people to sit in the viewing box, such as [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] of [[Sembla/Legends|Sembla]] [[Sweitt Concorkill/Legends|Sweitt Concorkill]] and [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].

It was there that Palpatine told Skywalker the story of [[Darth Plagueis/Legends|Darth Plagueis]], a story that would contribute to Anakin's fall to the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side of the Force]].

